version_description: Welcome to Spotify Stations!

What’s New
• Fixes for issues that could appear during times of limited connectivity
• Improvements to playback

Thanks for using Spotify Stations!

• Station edits are now saved automatically
• Support for additional languages
• Bug fixes and stability improvements

• You can now find recommended stations when looking at a Station's details
• Stability and bug fixes
